hooks.prompt:
Output valid JSON only. No markdown, no explanation, no code blocks.

If stop_hook_active is true: {"ok":true,"reason":"cleanup complete"}

Otherwise check session code for BLOCK violations: empty catch, silent error fallbacks, null returns without Optional, >4 params, commented-out code, copy-paste >5 lines, magic literals, framework in domain, dead code, clever one-liners, type switch >3 cases.

Clean: {"ok":true,"reason":"no violations"}
Violations found: {"ok":false,"reason":"[list violations briefly]"}
